title: Qeshlaq-e Alish
text: Qeshlaq-e Alish (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Qeshlāq-e Ālīsh) is a village in <a href="Anjirlu%20Rural%20District">Anjirlu Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Bileh%20Savar%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Bileh%20Savar%20County">Bileh Savar County</a>, <a href="Ardabil%20Province">Ardabil Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 19, in 5 families.
